{"type":"text","timestamp":1775897391832,"sessionID":"ses_284491adcffeLHpQLAseZVZ6d5","part":{"id":"prt_d7bbb8b46001yzdLeb4pBNP3XS","messageID":"msg_d7bbb5f68001tErBiOP1PXQx1p","sessionID":"ses_284491adcffeLHpQLAseZVZ6d5","type":"text","text":"I've created the design document for **AR-025 — MetadataService and Data Models** at `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/cmd/cli/design.md`.\n\nThe document includes comprehensive technical implementation details covering:\n\n## Key Components\n\n1. **AgentMetadata** (Pydantic BaseModel)\n   - Complete field definitions with types and defaults\n   - Field validators for `language`, `build_mode`, and `port`\n   - Model configuration for strict validation\n\n2. **MetadataOptions** (Dataclass)\n   - CLI option mapping to metadata fields\n   - `from_options()` factory method for dictionary conversion\n\n3. **MetadataService**\n   - `load_metadata()` - with fallback chain (agent_metadata.yaml → agent.yaml → metadata.yaml)\n   - `save_metadata()` - YAML persistence with proper formatting\n   - `update_metadata()` - partial updates with re-validation\n   - `validate_workspace()` - language-specific validation (Python/Java)\n   - `_create_default_metadata()` - automatic entrypoint inference\n\n## Additional Sections\n\n- **Data Models** - Complete schema tables for AgentMetadata and MetadataOptions\n- **YAML Output Format** - Example metadata file structure\n- **Error Handling** - Error types and handling patterns\n- **Configuration** - Environment variables and file locations\n- **Testing Strategy** - Unit tests, mock examples, and integration tests\n- **Security Considerations** - Credential handling, file permissions, path traversal protection\n- **Performance Characteristics** - Timing estimates and optimization strategies\n- **Dependencies** - Required packages (pydantic, pyyaml)\n\nThe design follows the same structure as the existing AR-024 (DockerService) document and integrates with the CLI specification from `cli-toolkit/spec.md`.","time":{"start":1775897391828,"end":1775897391828}}}
